snippet.title: Telefrag VR – Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Add Telefrag VR to your Steam Wishlist!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/916100/Telefrag_VR/

Start the battle on the abstract arenas, defying gravity. Choose the right weapon loadout for your fighting style. Master either the Dash or Smooth movement to climb the top in the cross-platform PvP matches. The gates for the Telefrag VR Tournament are opening on July 19th on Steam, Oculus Store and PlayStation Store!

---
